{"tid":783103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧龍威代表律師：鄧龍威被押至黑房隔離囚禁","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T14:58:17.000Z","uid":54733,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f613c9566714bca2d68659974c6e9fb4e2795d19","tid":783103,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:47:46.000Z","msg":"關注組指鄧龍威被押至黑房隔離囚禁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/DENG-PRISON-180817-16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FDENG-PRISON-180817-16.jpg&h=9e2879bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】鄧龍威事件關注組證實，鄧龍威因私藏手提電話及出書，驚動正在囚禁他的監獄獄長，被即時押至黑房隔離囚禁。<br />\n<br />\n事件關注組在社交平台指，鄧龍威代表律師表示，到監獄探訪發現他被隔離。鄧龍威準備了字條讓律師轉交給關注組，希望能聯絡駐菲律賓英國領事館尋求協助，又覺得事件已達至外交層面，被關押黑房是預計中的後果。<br />\n<br />\n港人鄧龍威十八年前在菲律賓捲入販毒案被判終身監禁，近日鄧龍威一方從菲律賓官方獲得新的翻案證據，行政長官林鄭月娥早前曾致函菲律賓總統杜特爾特，希望對方關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=316972\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D316972&d=bO0u9ZGjfLMWtTGwNArufDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=da0e3e03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D316972&h=0c9a771d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=316972</a>"},{"pid":"4ec9de01a70742342aaba1468f94063e978a74c2","tid":783103,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:03:01.000Z","msg":"多謝林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf30f43a264d6f8249cfb2c8928f8367db01b8a7","tid":783103,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"之前日日上舊登喊寃仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2354cace2191a60c2e8c67